Package org.openbel.framework.ws.dialect

Dialect-centric web services.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DialectFactory Factory class for creation of Dialects
 

Class Summary
CustomDialect Dialect implementation that allows control over the Namespace s used in conversion.
DefaultDialect Simple dialect that uses the BEL short form of the first supporting term found for a Kam.KamNode.
This implementation caches labels for nodes and is thus suitable only for a single Kam.
DialectFactoryImpl Service to construct Dialects.
This service will always create new Dialect instances.
 

Enum Summary
BELSyntax Defines the different syntaxes of BEL.
NamespaceDomain Constants for Namespace domains.
